videos.description: Binghamton guard Timmy Rose kicks it to Caleb Stewart for the 3-pointer as the shot clock winds down.
videos.headline: Stewart drains contested 3-pointer to pull ahead

videos.description: Michigan forward Isaiah Livers drives baseline and slams it home over Binghamton.
videos.headline: Livers rises over defender for dunk

videos.description: Isaiah Livers drives the lane for the layup score and the foul.
videos.headline: Michigan's Livers finishes through contact

videos.description: Brazdeikis drives into the paint and gets the layup and the foul.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis draws a foul and hits layup

videos.description: Michigan's Isaiah Livers hits a 3-pointer to put the Wolverines up by 14 over Binghamton.
videos.headline: Livers 3-pointer pushes Michigan lead to 14
